[{"id":"RAW_4aec841d","title":"语音智能体能否处理双语客户？前沿 ASR 在语码转换语音上的基准测试","link":"https://huggingface.co/blog/ServiceNow-AI/code-switching","date":"2026-06-10 03:38:28","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_4aec841d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Hugging Face - Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_cd02c457","title":"多媒体积木块","link":"https://huggingface.co/blog/mishig/spaces-agents-md","date":"2026-06-09 18:51:05","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_cd02c457.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Hugging Face - Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":4,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_8d85909c","title":"只给一份文档，Qwen3.7-Max 从 0 交付双端应用","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMTYyMTAzNA==&mid=2247501453&idx=1&sn=ba96a013175e2587878e1b2e00c9ab73","date":"2026-06-09 17:28:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_8d85909c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"通义实验室","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":21,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_bff54423","title":"Dario Amodei — 关于 AI 指数级发展的政策","link":"https://darioamodei.com/post/policy-on-the-ai-exponential","date":"2026-06-11 02:36:04","oneSentenceSummary":"Dario Amodei 认为 AI 正呈指数级发展，与缓慢的政策制定形成危险的不匹配，并提出了涵盖监管、经济、科学、公民自由和地缘政治等领域的具体行动方案以应对这一时刻。","summary":"在这篇文章中，Anthropic 的 CEO Dario Amodei 认为，AI 发展的指数级速度与政策和立法的缓慢步伐之间已形成一种紧迫的不匹配。他主张，AI 变革性力量及其风险的证据如今已无可否认，并以 Claude Mythos Preview 及其网络安全影响为例。文章在五个领域提出了一套全面的政策议程：1) 监管与公共安全，主张以 FAA 为蓝本，实施强制性第三方测试，并赋予政府阻止不安全前沿模型部署的权力；2) 宏观经济与税收政策，警告潜在的持久性劳动力替代，并提出促进就业的激励措施、工资保险和长期收入支持；3) 加速 AI 的积极影响，特别是在生物医学领域，呼吁进行监管改革以应对 AI 加速的药物发现；4) 国家与公民自由，提出自主武器的规则、堵住数据经纪商的漏洞，并确保公众获得 AI 建议的权利；以及 5) 地缘政治，认为 AI 是未来军事和经济实力的主导来源，民主国家必须确保其领导地位。该文章还附带了 Anthropic 发布的一项关于前沿模型测试的立法提案和一个关于就业替代的政策框架。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_bff54423.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Hacker News","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":24,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_d12e437d","title":"Salesforce 从 20，000 个企业智能体部署中学到的经验","link":"https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/what-salesforce-learned-from-20000","date":"2026-06-09 23:07:59","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_d12e437d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"ByteByteGo Newsletter","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":15,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_9a3cb912","title":"4000 行代码撑起一个 Agent 框架？nanobot 架构深度解析","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&mid=2247695857&idx=1&sn=7c2f39eed5649d1ef2ddc47fd767b1fe","date":"2026-06-09 08:45:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_9a3cb912.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"腾讯云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_8c4ea6fb","title":"循环工程","link":"https://addyo.substack.com/p/loop-engineering","date":"2026-06-08 22:31:21","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_8c4ea6fb.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Elevate","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_e50e1e1a","title":"横向拆解 Claude Code、Codex 等六大 Agent 上下文压缩策略后，我们做了第 7 个","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODYwMjI2MA==&mid=2649801845&idx=1&sn=25c1772d233048ad058811b25ff90a5b","date":"2026-06-08 17:36:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_e50e1e1a.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"腾讯技术工程","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":35,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_65c75585","title":"突发新闻，以及结局可能如何开始","link":"https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/breaking-news-and-how-the-end-might","date":"2026-06-11 00:16:05","oneSentenceSummary":"加里·马库斯认为 OpenAI 是最可能引发 AI 泡沫破裂的导火索，将其与 WeWork 相提并论，并指出其不可持续的烧钱速度、失败的保证金贷款以及“代币最大化”模式的终结是危险信号。","summary":"本文是 AI 评论家加里·马库斯的一份详细分析，分为三个部分。第一部分是对史蒂夫·艾斯曼（以《大空头》闻名）的一次有先见之明的采访，马库斯在其中指出 OpenAI 是最脆弱的 AI 巨头，警告其财务问题可能对整个科技行业（包括甲骨文和英伟达）引发“海啸”般的连锁反应。第二部分报道了最近倒下的两块“多米诺骨牌”：“代币最大化”时代（AI 公司亏本提供服务）的终结，以及软银试图以其持有的 OpenAI 股份为担保获取 60 亿美元保证金贷款的努力失败，这表明银行并不信任 OpenAI 的估值。第三部分提出了一个更新的情景：OpenAI 的 IPO 被撤回，导致一连串违约和重大的市场回调。马库斯将此描述为 AI 行业潜在的“歪心狼时刻”。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_65c75585.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Marcus on AI","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_f360573e","title":"Claude Fable 5：最强 AI 正在变成“特权资源”","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzNjE2NTI3NQ==&mid=2247492036&idx=1&sn=9504fe291c6ab96d6d91c46b50882c3d","date":"2026-06-10 19:23:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深度解读 Anthropic Claude Fable 5 发布，指出其标志性意义在于前沿 AI 正从「能力竞赛」转向「访问权竞赛」，最强模型不再只按价格分层，也开始按信任边界分层。","summary":"本文围绕 Anthropic 发布的 Claude Fable 5 与受限版本 Mythos 5，展开了一场关于前沿 AI 分配方式的深度讨论。文章首先介绍了 Fable 5 的 benchmark 表现与定价（Opus 4.8 的两倍），并引用 Simon Willison 的实测，将其定位为「慢、贵、但能啃硬任务」的大工程模型。核心分析聚焦于几个关键产品设计：fallback routing（安全路由机制，高风险请求回退到 Opus 4.8）、静默削弱争议（针对前沿 LLM 开发主题的不可见限制）、以及 30 天数据留存政策。文章进一步讨论了 Project Glasswing 在漏洞发现上的成果，并引用了 Nathan Lambert 的批评，指出 Anthropic 正在将「能力访问控制」包装成模型安全的一部分。最终，文章将 Fable 5 的发布视为一个分水岭，认为其标志着前沿 AI 的稀缺品从 token、上下文窗口转向了「能力、信任、合规」的组合，并提出了「谁来监督信任本身」的终极问题。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_f360573e.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"浮之静","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_dbfbe02b","title":"TIL：在 AgentsView 中为模型设置自定义价格","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Jun/9/agentsview-custom-model-price/#atom-everything","date":"2026-06-10 05:35:31","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_dbfbe02b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":1,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_ef2571d3","title":"Andrej Karpathy 的一段话","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Jun/9/andrej-karpathy/#atom-everything","date":"2026-06-10 03:03:10","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/06/RAW_ef2571d3.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE